Notes: Trailing 12-11 with 14:11 left in first half, SP went on 10-0 run over next
4:35 and led by at least five points the rest of the way...SP led 61-52 with
9:42 left and went on 12-2 run for 73-54 lead...SP's biggest lead was 89-60
before LC scored final seven points...SP ranked No. 1 in D3hoops.com poll.
Game.Officials: Andrew Gallion,  Don Baumgart,  Monica Sereda
